Prompt for tags whenever a bookmark is created or updated.
@item bmkx-tags-for-completion
Which tags are completion candidates: @code{current} (the default), a
list of specific tags, or a list of bookmark files.
@end vtable

@section Annotations

@vtable @code
@item bookmark-automatically-show-annotations
If non-nil, pop up the annotation when jumping.  Value @code{edit}
opens in edit mode; anything else non-nil opens read-only.
@item bmkx-annotation-modes-inherit-from
